## TypeScript

### ❌ NEVER do this:
```tsx
function handleClick(e: any) { ... }
const data: any = await fetch(...);
```

### ✅ ALWAYS do this:
```tsx
function handleClick(e: React.MouseEvent<HTMLButtonElement>) { ... }

interface ApiResponse {
  id: number;
  title: string;
}
const data: ApiResponse = await fetch(...).then(r => r.json());
```

