## Styling

### ✅ Use Tailwind with cn() utility:
```tsx
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils';

<div className={cn(
  "base-classes",
  isActive && "active-classes",
  isDisabled && "opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed"
)} />
```

### ✅ Status-based styling pattern:
```tsx
const statusClasses = {
  draft: 'status-draft',
  accepted: 'status-accepted ring-2 ring-green-500/50',
  rejected: 'status-rejected opacity-50 grayscale',
};

<Card className={cn("card-hover", statusClasses[status])} />
```
